// We need s[cl-k] == s[cr+k].
// s[cl-k] == s[2a+ln-1-cl+k] and s[cr+k] == s[2a+ln-1-cr-k].
// If 2a+ln-1-cl+k == cr+k, i.e., 2a+ln-1-cl == cr, i.e., cl+cr == 2a+ln-1, then done.
// Otherwise, we need a chain of equalities...

