  //    on the right. But this isn't guaranteed by the palindrome alone.
  //    Hmm actually, the expansion might stop sooner because s[rs-1] might
  //    mismatch with s[re+1] even though s[re+1] is still within the palindrome.
  //    Wait - but the expansion finds the MAXIMAL palindrome from this center,
  //    which is AT LEAST as long as any palindrome centered here, including
